* Image Properties SideBar:

   - Added signal/slots control between IE and main interface about "comments & tags" tab.
     Comments & tags set from main must be updated in IE and vise-versa.
   - Fix in IE/Showfoto Image Properties side bar restoration after fullscreen mode.
   
     
* 16 bits/color/pixels support : Any Image plugins must be adapted. Current port status is listed below :

   - BCG Adjust    (core plugin) : Done.
   - HSL Adjust    (core plugin) : Uncomplete. There is a problem in DImg::DColor with 16 bits images.
   - RGB Adjust    (core plugin) : Done.
   - Red Eyes      (core plugin) : Done
   - B&W Tool      (core plugin) : Done.
   - Blur Tool     (core plugin) : Done.
   - Sharpen Tool  (core plugin) : Done.
   - ICC Tool      (core plugin) : Done.
   - Ratio Crop    (core plugin) : Done.
   - Auto-Colors   (core plugin) : Done.

   - Adjust Curves   (digikamimageplugins) : Done.
   - Adjust Levels   (digikamimageplugins) : Done.
   - Anti Vignetting (digikamimageplugins) : Done.
   - Blowup          (digikamimageplugins) : Done.
   - Blur FX         (digikamimageplugins) : TODO.
   - Add Border      (digikamimageplugins) : TODO.
   - Channel Mixer   (digikamimageplugins) : Done.
   - Charcoal        (digikamimageplugins) : TODO.
   - Distortion FX   (digikamimageplugins) : TODO.
   - Emboss          (digikamimageplugins) : TODO.
   - Film Grain      (digikamimageplugins) : TODO.
